core

Class Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Invalidatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioListenerComponent, AudioSourceComponent, CameraComponent, DefaultLightComponent, MeshComponent, SplineComponent

    public abstract class Component
extends java.lang.Object
implements Invalidatable
    All of a GameObject's Components based on this abstract class. The GameLoop call it's update method once a frame, before rendering.
    See Also:
    GameObject
